Mongo Installation 

1. wget -qO - https://www.mongodb.org/static/pgp/server-6.0.asc | sudo apt-key add -

2. echo "deb [ arch=amd64,arm64 ] https://repo.mongodb.org/apt/ubuntu focal/mongodb-org/6.0 multiverse" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/mongodb-org-6.0.list

3. sudo apt-get update

4. sudo apt-get install -y mongodb-org

Step 4. if any error then follow these steps
	
	4.1 wget http://archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/main/o/openssl/libssl1.1_1.1.1f-1ubuntu2_amd64.deb
	4.2 sudo dpkg -i libssl1.1_1.1.1f-1ubuntu2_amd64.deb
	4.3 sudo apt-get install -y mongodb-org

Done ...